* WIP Complete manual
      Manual infrastructure (sb-texinfo + makeinfo) lives in master.
      Per-symbol .texinfo files in doc/include/ are auto-generated
      from docstrings; screamer.texinfo references them via @include.
      Build: cd doc && make clean && make all.
***** WIP All exported symbols documented.
        Was DONE on master. 4.0.1 added ~19 symbols that still need
        @include lines in screamer.texinfo: n-values, n-variables,
        n-lists-of-variables, mapcar-nondeterministic,
        map-nondeterministic, lambda-nondeterministic, optimize-value,
        a-rational{,-above,-below,-between},
        a-ratio{,-above,-below,-between}, a-rationalv, a-ratiov,
        a-floatv, a-random-member-of, a-random-member-ofv,
        rationalpv, ratiopv, floatpv, all-differentv, random-force.
        Docstrings already exist; only the @include lines are missing.
